name: SYNAP LOGIC
description: SynapLogic is an AI-powered Web3 game layer 2 ecosystem. As a pioneer in AI-driven solutions, SynapLogic integrates advanced artificial intelligence into its gaming experiences and tools, enhancing creativity and gameplay. Through its extensive network, SynapLogic develops, finances, acquires, publishes, and distributes games in collaboration with leading studios, focusing on immersive, high-quality Web3 gaming experiences within one interconnected ecosystem centered around the SYP token.
